5|$|After the war <b>the</b> <b>gun</b> <b>was</b> {{supplied}} to many {{countries around the}} globe, including former Warsaw Pact allies, such as Poland. As of the early 2000s it remains in service in Afghanistan, Albania, China, Cuba, Hungary, Iraq, Mozambique, Syria, Vietnam and other countries. <b>The</b> <b>gun</b> <b>was</b> employed in the Arab-Israeli Conflict and also in some conflicts in former republics of Soviet Union. The long operational history of D-1 howitzers in the national armies of numerous countries is an additional testimony to its qualities.|$|E
